methods.getCurrent:
Gets the current value of the ema.

:return: (double) current value of the ema.
methods.getLastTimestamp:
Gets the last time the ema was updated.

:return: (long) last time the ema was updated.
methods.setCurrent:
Sets the current value of the ema state.

:param value: (double) - new value of the ema state.

text: Base class for computing moving averages.
